Enum CDHOTSPOTBEGIN.Type

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<CDHOTSPOTBEGIN.Type>
      • org.openntf.domino.nsfdata.structs.cd.CDHOTSPOTBEGIN.Type
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<CDHOTSPOTBEGIN.Type>
    Enclosing class:
    CDHOTSPOTBEGIN

    public static enum CDHOTSPOTBEGIN.Type
extends Enum<CDHOTSPOTBEGIN.Type>
    These flags are used to define what type of hotspot is being defined by a CDHOTSPOTBEGIN data structure. (editods.h)
